The paper discusses the design of hybrid beamforming for millimeter-wave communication systems, which is a topic related to information theory (cs.IT), communication systems (cs.COMM), signal processing (cs.SI), network infrastructure (cs.NI), and multimedia (cs.MM). Therefore, these are the most likely arXiv CS sub-categories for this paper.
